# EH990-231331 - Workplace Category 6 Procurement RFP
### Procurement Details
| Item | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **Reference Number** | WS3756144921 |
| **Amendment Number** | 7 |
| **Publication Date** | January 31, 2023 |
| **Tender Closing Date** | March 3, 2023 @ 2:00 PM EST |
| **Expected Contract Start Date** | February 8, 2023 |
| **Region of Delivery** | National Capital Region (NCR), Ontario |

### Tender Description
Public Works and Government Services Canada’s Real Property Services Branch is seeking proposals for the purchase, delivery, and installation of office furniture between September 2023 and January 2024. 

### Important Notes
- A correction to the closing deadline: Please disregard the initial Ariba Discovery response and CanadaBuys posting deadlines. All supporting documentation and bid submissions must be completed by 2:00 PM EST on March 3, 2023. 

### Contact Information
| Item | Value |
| --- | --- |
| **End User Entity** | Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) |
| **Contracting Entity** | Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) |
| **Contact Person** | Michelle Wong (elle-la / she-her) |
| **Contact Email** | [michelle.wong@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:michelle.wong@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca) |
| **Access to Tender Documents** | SAP Ariba account required |

### Unspsc Classification
- Office tables 
- Conference tables
- Standing furniture
- Seating and stools 

### Additional Information
- The full Request for Bid (RFB) can be accessed and downloaded via the SAP Ariba account.
- Refer to the accompanying attachments for further details. 
- Failure to submit the bid in accordance with the specified terms and conditions may result in non-responsiveness.
